               libc6-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.0

Package: rack
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, init-system-helpers (>= 1.54~)
Description: RACK - Robotics Application Construction Kit
 Provides the TiMS (Tube IPC Message Service) real-time IPC backend used
 by CommRaT for inter-module message passing on Xenomai/EVL systems.
 Includes the tims_router_tcp systemd service, enabled on install.

Package: rack-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, rack
Description: RACK - development headers and static libraries
 Header files and link libraries for building applications against the
 RACK TiMS IPC system.

Package: rack-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, rack
Description: RACK - tools and example modules
 Additional utility binaries and scripts for the RACK framework.
